00:43:42.939 --> 00:43:45.642
that's my doing, and I certainly get it

1036
00:43:45.642 --> 00:43:48.144
when I'm on the road trying to get around someone,

1037
00:43:48.144 --> 00:43:51.513
I'll be projecting this horrible impatience

